PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,FPolice body worn camera footage shows
OL,8,Fthe moment PC Alice Beer was attacked
OL,9,Fby Guy Pottle
OL,11,FAn 'extremely dangerous' man has been
OL,12,Fjailed for ten and a half years for a
OL,13,Fviolent attack on a police officer
OL,14,Fwhich left her fearing for her life.
OL,16,FPC Alice Beer was "traumatised" after
OL,17,Fbeing hit in the face with a bottle
OL,18,Fand forced over the railings of a
OL,19,Ffirst floor balcony during the assault
OL,20,Fin February this year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,FPC Beer was called to help Guy Pottle,
OL,8,Fwho was on the wrong side of balcony
OL,9,Frailings in Newton Abbot.
OL,11,FAs she held onto his right arm, she
OL,12,Fdidn't know he was holding a bottle in
OL,13,Fhis other hand.
OL,15,FAs she backed away he then approached
OL,16,Fher, grabbed her, and tried to force
OL,17,Fher head-first over the railings.
OL,19,FSomehow, and she still doesn't know
OL,20,Fquite how, she managed to hang on.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,F'Am I going to die?'
OL,9,FStill in her first year of service,
OL,10,FAlice is now back on duty at work, but
OL,11,Fshe says she doesn't feel she will
OL,12,Fever move on from it completely.
OL,14,FShe told ITV West Country: "That
OL,15,Fmoment where he locked eyes with me
OL,16,Fand then bottled me with a glass
OL,17,Fbottle - and then he almost managed to
OL,18,Fpush me over the railings - my only
OL,19,Fthought at that moment was 'I am going
OL,20,Fto die?'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,F"That's quite a scary thought."
OL,9,FAlice had six weeks off work. She has
OL,10,Fcuts to her face, one over her eye
OL,11,Fwhere the bottle hit, cuts in her eye
OL,12,Ffrom the glass and from being punched
OL,13,Fmultiple times in the face, and cuts
OL,14,Fand bruises on her arms.
OL,16,FSpeaking tearfully in court on Friday,
OL,17,FPC Beer said the assault was something
OL,18,Fshe will never forget.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,F"I was signed off work for my injuries
OL,8,Fand wellbeing, to physically recover
OL,9,Fand process what had happened to me,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,F"It is possible I will be left with
OL,13,Fpost-traumatic stress disorder.
OL,15,F"This has really impacted my self-
OL,16,Fconfidence. I have questioned whether
OL,17,FI can remain in this profession, which
OL,18,FI have worked so hard for."
OL,20,F'Assault is unacceptable'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,FSenior officers say assaults like this
OL,8,Fon police or other emergency service
OL,9,Fworkers are unacceptable.
OL,11,FChief Superintendent Roy Linden said:
OL,12,F"We know when we sign up for the job
OL,13,Fthat often we will walk towards to
OL,14,Frisk.
OL,16,F"We don't do so ignorant of what those
OL,17,Frisks are, but we do not accept being
OL,18,Fassaulted as part of our day job.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,F"Our officers provide a high-quality
OL,8,Fservice to the public and demonstrate
OL,9,Fpersonal commitment, dedication and
OL,10,Fcourage on a daily basis and I have
OL,11,Fnothing but praise for all those at
OL,12,Fthe scene during what were some
OL,13,Fextremely difficult and challenging
OL,14,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,F"While the nature of policing brings
OL,8,Finherent risks with it, being
OL,9,Fassaulted on duty should never be
OL,10,Fcondoned or seen as 'part of the job'
OL,11,Fand any injury to an officer on duty
OL,12,Fis treated with the utmost
OL,13,Fseriousness."
OL,15,F'I am not the same person'
OL,17,FPC Beer says she doesn't want this
OL,18,Fincident to define her whole career
OL,19,Fwhen it is still at such an early
OL,20,Fstage.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,F"Ever since it happened I said I don't
OL,8,Fwant to let what's happened ruin it
OL,9,Ffor me," she said.
OL,11,F"He's not ruining what I really, truly
OL,12,Fbelieve is the best job in the world.
OL,14,F"I'm not the same person I was before.
OL,15,FI've always got that ball in my
OL,16,Fstomach where I am a bit anxious, but
OL,17,FI am really enjoying being back at
OL,18,Fwork and being back with my team. They
OL,19,Fare the best team in the world really."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,F39 year old Guy Pottle pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto unlawful wounding and attempted GBH.
OL,10,FHe was jailed for ten years and six
OL,11,Fmonths, with an extended licence
OL,12,Fperiod of another five years.
OL,14,FHe was told he would serve two thirds
OL,15,Fof his sentence before becoming
OL,16,Feligible for parole.
OL,18,F'You attacked a public servant'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,FPassing sentence, His Honour Judge
OL,8,FJames Patrick told Pottle: "You are an
OL,9,Fextremely dangerous man and the public
OL,10,Fneeds to be protected from you.
OL,12,F'I accept that you have had a
OL,13,Fdifficult life with a difficult
OL,14,Fbackground. You appeared that night to
OL,15,Fbe suicidal.
OL,17,F'It's plain that you intended PC Alice
OL,18,FBeer to go head first over the
OL,19,Fbalcony. You plainly intended to cause
OL,20,Fher very serious harm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1782818297
OL,3,CMan jailed for ten years for trying to
OL,4,Cthrow female police officer over
OL,5,Cbalcony
OL,7,F'She would have suffered life-changing
OL,8,Finjuries. You were attacking a public
OL,9,Fservant who was trying to come to
OL,10,Fhelp.'
OL,12,FTurning to PC Beer, the Judge said:
OL,13,F"May I commend you for your service
OL,14,Fand your bravery."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
